{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"canvas","mdn_url":"/es/docs/Web/HTML/Element/canvas","locale":"es","native":"Español","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p><span class=\"goog-gtc-unit\" id=\"goog-gtc-unit-4\"><span class=\"goog-gtc-from-human goog-gtc-translatable\" dir=\"ltr\">El elemento HTML <em>canvas</em> (&lt;canvas&gt;) se puede utilizar para dibujar gráficos a través de secuencias de comandos (por lo general <a href=\"/../../../../en/JavaScript\" rel=\"internal\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">JavaScript</a> ).</span></span> <span class=\"goog-gtc-unit\" id=\"goog-gtc-unit-5\"><span class=\"goog-gtc-from-human goog-gtc-translatable\" dir=\"ltr\">Por ejemplo, puede usarse para dibujar gráficos, hacer composiciones de fotos o incluso realizar animaciones.</span></span></p>\n\n<p>\n </p><p><span class=\"goog-gtc-unit\" id=\"goog-gtc-unit-6\"><span class=\"goog-gtc-from-human goog-gtc-translatable\" dir=\"ltr\">Las aplicaciones de Mozilla adquirieron la compatibilidad con <code>&lt;canvas&gt;</code> a partir de Gecko 1.8 (es decir, <a href=\"/../../../../en/Firefox_1.5_for_developers\" rel=\"internal\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">Firefox 1.5</a> ).</span></span> <span class=\"goog-gtc-unit\" id=\"goog-gtc-unit-7\"><span class=\"goog-gtc-from-human goog-gtc-translatable\" dir=\"ltr\">El elemento fue originalmente introducido por Apple en el OS X <a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.apple.com/macosx/features/dashboard/\" rel=\"external nofollow noopener\">Dashboard</a> y Safari.</span></span> <span class=\"goog-gtc-unit\" id=\"goog-gtc-unit-8\"><span class=\"goog-gtc-from-human goog-gtc-translatable\" dir=\"ltr\">Internet Explorer, antes de la versión 9.0 beta, no admite de forma nativa <code>&lt;canvas&gt;</code> , pero una página puede de hecho añadir la compatibilidad mediante la inclusión de un script del proyecto <a class=\"external\" href=\"http://excanvas.sourceforge.net/\" rel=\"external nofollow noopener\">Explorer Canvas</a> de Google.</span></span> <span class=\"goog-gtc-unit\" id=\"goog-gtc-unit-9\"><span class=\"goog-gtc-from-mt goog-gtc-translatable\" dir=\"ltr\">Opera 9 también es compatible con <code>&lt;canvas&gt;</code> .</span></span></p>\n\n\n<p><span class=\"goog-gtc-unit\" id=\"goog-gtc-unit-10\"><span class=\"goog-gtc-from-human goog-gtc-translatable\" dir=\"ltr\">Para más artículos sobre canvas, consulta la <a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Canvas_API\" title=\"es/HTML/Canvas\">página del tema canvas</a> .</span></span></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"contexto_de_uso","title":"<span class=\"goog-gtc-unit\" id=\"goog-gtc-unit-11\"><span class=\"goog-gtc-from-tm goog-gtc-from-tm-score-100 goog-gtc-translatable\" dir=\"ltr\">Contexto de uso</span></span>","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><span class=\"goog-gtc-unit\" id=\"goog-gtc-unit-12\"><span class=\"goog-gtc-from-tm goog-gtc-from-tm-score-100 goog-gtc-translatable\" dir=\"ltr\">Contenido permitido</span></span></td>\n   <td><span class=\"goog-gtc-unit\" id=\"goog-gtc-unit-13\"><span class=\"goog-gtc-from-human goog-gtc-translatable\" dir=\"ltr\">Transparente, ya sea <a href=\"/en-US/HTML/Content_categories#phrasing_content\" title=\"en/HTML/Content categories#phrasing content\">contenido estático</a> o <a href=\"/en-US/HTML/Content_categories#flow_content\" title=\"en/HTML/Content categories#flow content\">contenido dinámico</a> .</span></span></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><span class=\"goog-gtc-unit\" id=\"goog-gtc-unit-14\"><span class=\"goog-gtc-from-tm goog-gtc-from-tm-score-100 goog-gtc-translatable\" dir=\"ltr\">Omisión de etiquetas</span></span></td>\n   <td><span class=\"goog-gtc-unit\" id=\"goog-gtc-unit-15\"><span class=\"goog-gtc-from-human goog-gtc-translatable\" dir=\"ltr\">Ninguna, deben estar presentes tanto las etiquetas de inicio como las de cierre</span></span></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><span class=\"goog-gtc-unit\" id=\"goog-gtc-unit-16\"><span class=\"goog-gtc-from-tm goog-gtc-from-tm-score-100 goog-gtc-translatable\" dir=\"ltr\">Elementos primarios permitidos</span></span></td>\n   <td><span class=\"goog-gtc-unit\" id=\"goog-gtc-unit-17\"><span class=\"goog-gtc-from-human goog-gtc-ph-missing goog-gtc-translatable\" dir=\"ltr\">Cualquier elemento que acepte contenido dinámico o cualquier otro elemento que acepte contenido estático .</span></span>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><span class=\"goog-gtc-unit\" id=\"goog-gtc-unit-18\"><span class=\"goog-gtc-from-tm goog-gtc-from-tm-score-100 goog-gtc-translatable\" dir=\"ltr\">Documento normativo</span></span></td>\n   <td><a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/html5/the-canvas-element.html#the-canvas-element\" rel=\" noopener\"><span class=\"goog-gtc-unit\" id=\"goog-gtc-unit-19\"><span class=\"goog-gtc-from-mt goog-gtc-translatable\" dir=\"ltr\">HTML 5, sección 4.8.10</span></span></a></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>","titleAsText":"Contexto de uso"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"atributos","title":"<span class=\"goog-gtc-unit\" id=\"goog-gtc-unit-20\"><span class=\"goog-gtc-from-tm goog-gtc-from-tm-score-100 goog-gtc-translatable\" dir=\"ltr\">Atributos</span></span>","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"width\"><span class=\"goog-gtc-unit\" id=\"goog-gtc-unit-21\"><span class=\"goog-gtc-from-tm goog-gtc-from-tm-score-100 goog-gtc-translatable\" dir=\"ltr\"><a id=\"attr-width\" href=\"#attr-width\"><b><code>width</code></b></a></span></span></dt>\n <dd>&nbsp;<span class=\"goog-gtc-unit\" id=\"goog-gtc-unit-22\"><span class=\"goog-gtc-from-mt goog-gtc-translatable\" dir=\"ltr\">La anchura del espacio de coordenadas en píxeles CSS.</span></span> <span class=\"goog-gtc-unit\" id=\"goog-gtc-unit-23\"><span class=\"goog-gtc-from-mt goog-gtc-translatable\" dir=\"ltr\">El valor predeterminado es 300.</span></span></dd>\n <dt id=\"height\"><span class=\"goog-gtc-unit\" id=\"goog-gtc-unit-24\"><span class=\"goog-gtc-from-tm goog-gtc-from-tm-score-100 goog-gtc-translatable\" dir=\"ltr\"><a id=\"attr-height\" href=\"#attr-height\"><b><code>height</code></b></a></span></span></dt>\n <dd><span class=\"goog-gtc-unit\" id=\"goog-gtc-unit-25\"><span class=\"goog-gtc-from-mt goog-gtc-translatable\" dir=\"ltr\">La altura del espacio de coordenadas en píxeles CSS.</span></span> <span class=\"goog-gtc-unit\" id=\"goog-gtc-unit-26\"><span class=\"goog-gtc-from-mt goog-gtc-translatable\" dir=\"ltr\">El valor predeterminado es 150.</span></span></dd>\n</dl>\n\n<div class=\"note notecard\" id=\"sect1\"><span class=\"goog-gtc-unit\" id=\"goog-gtc-unit-27\"><span class=\"goog-gtc-from-human goog-gtc-translatable\" dir=\"ltr\">Nota: el tamaño del lienzo mostrado se puede cambiar con una hoja de estilo.</span></span> <span class=\"goog-gtc-unit\" id=\"goog-gtc-unit-28\"><span class=\"goog-gtc-from-human goog-gtc-translatable\" dir=\"ltr\">La imagen se escala durante la representación para adaptarse al tamaño que se le ha aplicado estilo .</span></span></div>","titleAsText":"Atributos"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"interfaz_dom","title":"<span class=\"goog-gtc-unit\" id=\"goog-gtc-unit-29\"><span class=\"goog-gtc-from-tm goog-gtc-from-tm-score-99 goog-gtc-translatable\" dir=\"ltr\">Interfaz DOM</span></span>","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/DOM/HTMLCanvasElement\" title=\"en/DOM/HTMLCanvasElement\"><span class=\"goog-gtc-unit\" id=\"goog-gtc-unit-30\"><span class=\"goog-gtc-from-mt goog-gtc-translatable\" dir=\"ltr\">HTMLCanvasElement</span></span></a></li>\n</ul>","titleAsText":"Interfaz DOM"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"ejemplo","title":"<span class=\"goog-gtc-unit\"><span class=\"goog-gtc-from-mt goog-gtc-translatable\" dir=\"ltr\">Ejemplo</span></span>","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>canvas</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">id</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>canvas<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">width</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>300<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">height</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>300<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  Tu navegador no admite el elemento <span class=\"token entity named-entity\" title=\"<\">&amp;lt;</span>canvas<span class=\"token entity named-entity\" title=\">\">&amp;gt;</span>.\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>canvas</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>","titleAsText":"Ejemplo"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"sobre_accesibilidad","title":"Sobre Accesibilidad","isH3":false,"content":"<p>El elemento <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/canvas\" title=\"Use the HTML <canvas> element with either the canvas scripting API or the WebGL API to draw graphics and animations.\"><code>&lt;canvas&gt;</code></a> es simplemente un bitman que no provee ninguna información adicional sobre los elementos que tiene dibujados. El contenido de la etiqueta <code>canvas</code> no se muestra a los lectores de pantalla como otras etiquetas semánticas. Como regla general, deberías evitar utilizar canvas en un sitio accesible.</p>\n\n<p>Para mejorar la accesibilidad de la etiquetas puedes leer los siguientes artículos (en inglés):</p>\n\n<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Canvas_API/Tutorial/Hit_regions_and_accessibility\">MDN Hit regions and accessability</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/WAI/PF/HTML/wiki/Canvas_Accessibility_Use_Cases\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Canvas accessibility use cases</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/html/wg/wiki/AddedElementCanvas\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Canvas element accessibility issues</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"http://www.paciellogroup.com/blog/2012/06/html5-canvas-accessibility-in-firefox-13/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML5 Canvas Accessibility in Firefox 13 – by Steve Faulkner</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/scripting.html#best-practices\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Best practices for interactive canvas elements</a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"consulta_también","title":"<span class=\"goog-gtc-unit\" id=\"goog-gtc-unit-31\"><span class=\"goog-gtc-from-tm goog-gtc-from-tm-score-100 goog-gtc-translatable\" dir=\"ltr\">Consulta también</span></span>","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Canvas_API\" title=\"es/HTML/Canvas\"><span class=\"goog-gtc-unit\" id=\"goog-gtc-unit-32\"><span class=\"goog-gtc-from-human goog-gtc-translatable\" dir=\"ltr\">Tema sobre canvas</span></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; text-indent: 0px;\"><span style=\"color: #000000; font-family: 'Ubuntu'; font-size: 9pt;\"></span></p>","titleAsText":"Consulta también"}}],"toc":[{"text":"<span class=\"goog-gtc-unit\" id=\"goog-gtc-unit-11\"><span class=\"goog-gtc-from-tm goog-gtc-from-tm-score-100 goog-gtc-translatable\" dir=\"ltr\">Contexto de uso</span></span>","id":"contexto_de_uso"},{"text":"<span class=\"goog-gtc-unit\" id=\"goog-gtc-unit-20\"><span class=\"goog-gtc-from-tm goog-gtc-from-tm-score-100 goog-gtc-translatable\" dir=\"ltr\">Atributos</span></span>","id":"atributos"},{"text":"<span class=\"goog-gtc-unit\" id=\"goog-gtc-unit-29\"><span class=\"goog-gtc-from-tm goog-gtc-from-tm-score-99 goog-gtc-translatable\" dir=\"ltr\">Interfaz DOM</span></span>","id":"interfaz_dom"},{"text":"<span class=\"goog-gtc-unit\"><span class=\"goog-gtc-from-mt goog-gtc-translatable\" dir=\"ltr\">Ejemplo</span></span>","id":"ejemplo"},{"text":"Sobre Accesibilidad","id":"sobre_accesibilidad"},{"text":"<span class=\"goog-gtc-unit\" id=\"goog-gtc-unit-31\"><span class=\"goog-gtc-from-tm goog-gtc-from-tm-score-100 goog-gtc-translatable\" dir=\"ltr\">Consulta también</span></span>","id":"consulta_también"}],"summary":"El elemento HTML canvas (<canvas>) se puede utilizar para dibujar gráficos a través de secuencias de comandos (por lo general JavaScript ). Por ejemplo, puede usarse para dibujar gráficos, hacer composiciones de fotos o incluso realizar animaciones.","popularity":0.0008,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"<canvas>","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch"},{"title":"<canvas>: The Graphics Canvas element","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"<canvas> : l'élément de canevas graphique","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"<canvas>: グラフィックキャンバス要素","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"<canvas>: 그래픽 캔버스 요소","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"canvas","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"<canvas>","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"<canvas>","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"},{"title":"<canvas>","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)"}],"source":{"folder":"es/web/html/element/canvas","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/es/web/html/element/canvas/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/es/docs/Web","title":"Tecnología para desarrolladores web"},{"uri":"/es/docs/Web/HTML","title":"HTML: Lenguaje de etiquetas de hipertexto"},{"uri":"/es/docs/Web/HTML/Element","title":"Referencia de Elementos HTML"},{"uri":"/es/docs/Web/HTML/Element/canvas","title":"canvas"}],"pageTitle":"canvas - HTML: Lenguaje de etiquetas de hipertexto | MDN","noIndexing":false}}